\">..</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Guest</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ends_with</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"gmail.com\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"no\">Admin</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ow\">or</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Guest</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ends_with</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"gmail.com\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"no\">Admin</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Guest</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ends_with</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"gmail.com\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"no\">Admin</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Guest</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ends_with</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"gmail.com\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"no\">Admin</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Guest</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ends_with</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"gmail.com\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"no\">Admin</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ow\">or</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Guest</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ends_with</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"gmail.com\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Here's I think the entire design space that has been talked about</p>",
        "id": 501083557,
        "sender_full_name": "Anthony Bullard",
        "timestamp": 1740137599
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Btw, wanted to note that it’s kinda inconsistent that tag unions are declared as <code>[A, B, C]</code> but pattern matched as <code>A | B | C</code>. Is it reasonable to align them somehow? I feel absolutely comfortable with the status quo, just want to give another perspective to the problem in the thread</p>",
        "id": 501093757,
        "sender_full_name": "Kiryl Dziamura",
        "timestamp": 1740140969
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It feels like making the types use pipes would be a great alignment, but it's don't know how to represent type extensions there</p>",
        "id": 501098153,
        "sender_full_name": "Sam Mohr",
        "timestamp": 1740142379
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I definitely don't think we should use <code>+</code>. People expect plus to do something. And in some cases it might (especially with operator overloading in the future)</p>\n<p><code>Red + Blue</code> is that two patterns or is that a custom type addition that will result in <code>Purple</code>?</p>",
        "id": 501150556,
        "sender_full_name": "Brendan Hansknecht",
        "timestamp": 1740158074
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I like how terse and simple <code>|</code> is. I think non-text is easier to format nicely than chains of text like would exist with <code>or</code></p>",
        "id": 501150718,
        "sender_full_name": "Brendan Hansknecht",
        "timestamp": 1740158135
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But I think I would be fine with any of <code>|</code>, <code>or</code>, and <code>,</code></p>",
        "id": 501150852,
        "sender_full_name": "Brendan Hansknecht",
        "timestamp": 1740158167
    }
